    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes so once we merge on master we do:\n- run the tests\n- wait for the release to be available on jsdelivr (automatically)\n- clear the cdn cache\n- regenerate the docs website (jsdocs were already generated on npm run release)\n- push to gh-pages the updated website\n- regenerate the jekyll search index\n\nSo the new release process is .. npm run release on master\n",
