    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yep, I got the gist of the process, my questions were more:\n- Who run the tests? Is that locally on the machine doing the push or on Travis?\n- How do you wait for the release to be available? Do you get a pingback or do you need to poll? Also, how long does it usually take?\n\nAfter that I guess this is a dance between GitHub and Travis. Travis builds the new website, pushes it to `gh-pages`, wich triggers a new Travis build that will update the search index?\n",
